snippet.title: Playne Gameplay : Meditation Nature Ambiance with Quotes
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage of Playne's meditation summary. Nature ambiance with wind and leaves of trees and looping quotes. Good if you want some relaxing ambiance to meditate to.

Playne: https://store.steampowered.com/app/865540/

Authors of quotes include:
Ramana MaharshiRalph
Waldo Emerson
J Krishnamurti
Nisargadatta Maharaj
